Dear Dr New Clinician-0,
The Az 1 TeamCoord at Org A set up your account on Patients Know Best so that you can help your patients online.

To get started, you need to complete your registration on the Patients Know Best website, so please click on this link:

http://pkb-frontend-8/clinicianRegistrationUserForm.action?icode=team_az&uid=2144&temp=f7iazVvKPz

After that, you can use Patients Know Best to work. Welcome to our site; we hope you like it!

Please do not reply to this email; this address is not monitored. Click this link to log into your record.

Yours,

Patients Know Best Help Team

Dear Dr New Clinician-1,
The Az 1 TeamCoord at Org A set up your account on Patients Know Best so that you can help your patients online.

To get started, you need to complete your registration on the Patients Know Best website, so please click on this link:

http://pkb-frontend-8/clinicianRegistrationUserForm.action?icode=team_az&uid=2150&temp=A7AlyMheaH

After that, you can use Patients Know Best to work. Welcome to our site; we hope you like it!

Please do not reply to this email; this address is not monitored. Click this link to log into your record.

Yours,

Patients Know Best Help Team

Dear Dr New Clinician-2,
The Az 1 TeamCoord at Org A set up your account on Patients Know Best so that you can help your patients online.

To get started, you need to complete your registration on the Patients Know Best website, so please click on this link:

http://pkb-frontend-8/clinicianRegistrationUserForm.action?icode=team_az&uid=2156&temp=k2C8VL7skF

After that, you can use Patients Know Best to work. Welcome to our site; we hope you like it!

Please do not reply to this email; this address is not monitored. Click this link to log into your record.

Yours,

Patients Know Best Help Team

Dear Dr New Clinician-4,
The Az 1 TeamCoord at Org A set up your account on Patients Know Best so that you can help your patients online.

To get started, you need to complete your registration on the Patients Know Best website, so please click on this link:

http://pkb-frontend-8/clinicianRegistrationUserForm.action?icode=team_az&uid=2168&temp=LFbesSMIO0

After that, you can use Patients Know Best to work. Welcome to our site; we hope you like it!

Please do not reply to this email; this address is not monitored. Click this link to log into your record.

Yours,

Patients Know Best Help Team

Dear Dr New Clinician-5,
The Az 1 TeamCoord at Org A set up your account on Patients Know Best so that you can help your patients online.

To get started, you need to complete your registration on the Patients Know Best website, so please click on this link:

Please do not reply to this email; this address is not monitored. Click this link to log into your record.

Patients Know Best Help Team

Dear Dr New Clinician-6,
The Az 1 TeamCoord at Org A set up your account on Patients Know Best so that you can help your patients online.

To get started, you need to complete your registration on the Patients Know Best website, so please click on this link:

http://pkb-frontend-8/clinicianRegistrationUserForm.action?icode=team_az&uid=2180&temp=kZ82sVCx4n

After that, you can use Patients Know Best to work. Welcome to our site; we hope you like it!

Please do not reply to this email; this address is not monitored. Click this link to log into your record.

Yours,

Patients Know Best Help Team

Dear Dr New Clinician-0,
The Az 1 TeamCoord at Org A set up your account on Patients Know Best so that you can help your patients online.

To get started, you need to complete your registration on the Patients Know Best website, so please click on this link:

http://pkb-frontend-8/clinicianRegistrationUserForm.action?icode=team_az&uid=2192&temp=aJBpGaO7MI

After that, you can use Patients Know Best to work. Welcome to our site; we hope you like it!

Please do not reply to this email; this address is not monitored. Click this link to log into your record.

Yours,

Patients Know Best Help Team
